Package: detectRUNS
Type: Package
Title: Detect Runs of Homozygosity (RoHom) and Runs of Heterozygosity (RoHet) in diploid genomes
Version: 0.4.6
Date: 2016-11-15
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Filippo Biscarini <filippo.biscarini@ptp.it> [aut, cre]",
    "Gabriele Marras <gabriele.marras@ptp.it> [aut]",
    "Paolo Cozzi <paolo.cozzi@ptp.it> [ctb]"
  ))
Description: Detection of RUNS of Homozygosity (RoHom) and of Heterozygosity (RoHet) using two methods:
  i) a method based on sliding windows (e.g. see Bjelland et al. 2013);
  ii) a method based on consecutive scan of loci along the genome (e.g. see Marras et al. 2015)
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    plyr,
    iterators,
    itertools,
    ggplot2,
    reshape2,
    Rcpp,
    data.table
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
